Ability.Description:
During a hunt, if all of the following three criteria are satisfied:

1. The fuse box is turned on;
2. The Jinn has line-of-sight with a player it is targeting;
3. The Jinn is further than 3 metres from that player.

Then its speed will be fixed at 2.5 m/s while the criteria are met. Otherwise, it will obey standard ghost speeds.
